verses.text: Ex schecab' Jehová, alec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová chi'. Alec wach' lolonel t'ay mach ex tze tanhvej stemplo tzek' ak'val.
Iq'uecq'ue van e k'ab' t'a stojolal scajnub' Jehová, tzeyalan wach' lolonel t'ay.
Ha Jehová b'oannac satcha’anh yet' lum lum tik, aocab' tz'ak'ancot svach'k'olal t'a eyib'anh masanto t'a lum tzalan Sion.
